						               													<description>Join your partner on a virtual island couples retreat, where you&amp;rsquo;re sure to have fun while building a better relationship! Just one round of play will show you why 86% of couples report significant benefits from using the Gottman approach to create stronger, deeper bonds between you and your sweetie.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Designed for couples who want to deepen their relationship and have fun together. Partners take turns rolling the dice and moving their game pieces with the goal of &amp;ldquo;returning home&amp;rdquo; from vacation with more closeness and intimacy.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Strengthen your relationship and deepen your connection by playing together in a tropical paradise! The Gottman Couples Retreat Board Game unites the best of our renowned, research-based relationship tools in a playful, accessible format. Balancing thoughtful conversation topics with fun, intimate action items, this &amp;quot;retreat&amp;quot; makes exploring each other's worlds enjoyable and enlightening. Even more, you'll be making deposits in your &amp;quot;Emotional Bank Account&amp;quot; by building on positive moments with each other during gameplay. Whether you're new partners or have been married for decades, the Gottman Couples Retreat Board Game is ideal for an at-home date night....or use it on anniversaries as a &amp;quot;ritual of connection&amp;quot; in your relationship. Also makes a special birthday gift or wedding present!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game ends when the ship field is reached.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
